title: 09/08/21 DPS Best Of
itunes:title: 09/08/21 DPS Best Of
description:
In this Best Of The Dan Patrick Show, Dan talks to former UCF and current Florida State quarterback McKenzie Milton about playing in his first game since his leg injury in 2018. Also, UCLA head football coach Chip Kelly calls in to talk about the Bruins' big win against LSU. And Presbyterian College head football coach Kevin Kelley explains why he doesn't like to punt.
